channel.title: What Am I Doing Wrong?!?!
channel.description: Okay, here's the problem, it's a pretty big one! I Can't play Mopar!!! I've tried countless times, and nothing works! I've downloaded it, and I start it up fine, then I go to the server status checker, find one, copy IP, paste into File>New Server>OK and then type in a user/pass. Nothing works, ever! All It says is either "Unexpected Server Response", "Error connecting to server. Must be down. Click 'Cancel' then 'Start Server' to make your own." So I do that and I get "Your account is already logged in. Try again right now, or make another one." And trust me, I've made account names nobody has ever thought of. But I CAN'T GET IN!! How can people say this is good?!!? I doubt they get to play it!! But If anyone can help me, I'd gladly appreciate it. And don't ask me about specs and whatnot, I'm good with computers, just not that good. :P
